author: Monica Sisavat
title: Jamie Dornan and Dakota Johnson's Oscars Enounter Might Make You Cringe a Little
text:
Jamie Dornan and Dakota Johnson at the 2017 Oscars Video Jamie Dornan and Dakota Johnson's Oscars Encounter Might Make You Cringe a Little February 26, 2017 by Monica Sisavat 2 Shares 
Jamie Dornan attended Sunday's Oscars in LA, and in addition to sharing several swoon-worthy moments with wife Amelia Warner on the red carpet, he also had an awkward encounter with Dakota Johnson . Before presenting the award for best production design, Dakota looked over at her Fifty Shades Darker costar and said, "You look familiar," to which Jamie replied, "I'm sure I do." You really just need to see the whole thing yourself.
